A government that covers the deficit, an election and a new government takes office.
Prodi did it in Italy after Berlusconi and Sócrates in Portugal after Durão Barroso.
It makes no sense for Ecofin to bail out Hungary from defaulting on foreign payments at the start of the year and to allow a euro member country to default on its obligations.
